Slow down.

00:45:30.240 --> 00:45:32.200
[Got a great idea! Definitely gonna work.]

00:45:32.440 --> 00:45:33.320
[Didn't you say "we all have a place"]

00:45:33.320 --> 00:45:33.920
["in this world"?]

