What does that matter?

00:46:23.080 --> 00:46:24.160
That got nothing to do with you.

00:46:24.160 --> 00:46:25.400
Those are just packaging.

00:46:25.560 --> 00:46:26.960
You're a doctor

00:46:26.960 --> 00:46:29.160
from the Royal College of Toronto.

00:46:29.880 --> 00:46:31.680
You just need to figure out

00:46:31.680 --> 00:46:33.040
the chemical composition inside,

00:46:33.040 --> 00:46:34.200
like the molecules and stuff.

00:46:34.200 --> 00:46:35.200
You figure that out,

00:46:35.200 --> 00:46:36.200
and that's it.

